info.author: 51Degrees
classifiers: License :: OSI Approved :: European Union Public Licence 1.2 (EUPL 1.2)
Topic :: Software Development :: Libraries :: Python Modules
info.name: fiftyone-pipeline-core
info.summary: The 51Degrees Pipeline API is a generic web request intelligence and data processing solution with the ability to add a range of 51Degrees and/or custom plug ins (Engines). This package definds the essential components of the Pipeline API such as flow elements, flow data and evidence. It also packages together JavaScript served by a pipeline and allows for client side requests for additional data populated by evidence from the client side.
